  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large wok over medium high heat",
    "Add the roasted garlic and cook for 1 minute",
    "Add the egg noodles and cook for 2 minutes",
    "Add the yuzu juice and coconut milk and stir to combine",
    "Bring the mixture to a simmer and cook for 5 minutes",
    "Season with salt and black pepper to taste",
    "Garnish with chopped scallions and serve hot",
    "Stir constantly to prevent the noodles from sticking to the wok"
